item.title: CVE-2023-1183|2023-07-10T15:04:30.740Z -- n%2Fa -- libreoffice
item.description: A flaw was found in the Libreoffice package. An attacker can craft an odb containing a "database/script" file with a SCRIPT command where the contents of the file could be written to a new file whose location was determined by the attacker.
